page.content:
CHILDRENS HOBBIES
My hobbies in the 1980's
My hobbies are gym, Trampoling and reading. I took up trampoling because I went to watch my sister and I thought it was good and so I started. I have been going for about a year now and I am already a Southern and British Champion. I like trampolining and I think it is very good fun. My second hobby is gymnaastics I started gymnastics when I saw it on the television and I thought it was really, really good. I go to gym once a week and I go trampolining twice a week.
